						<p>This inscription refers to the gift of land as <hi rend="italic">dēvadānam</hi> to the temple of Śivadharmīśvara[mu*]ḍaiya Mahādēvar by Kōlaṉ Tirukkoḍuṅguṉṟa muḍaiyāṉ <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Nishadharājaṉ of Poṉṉamarāvati in Puramalaināḍu.</p>						

